      <title>巴西部分地区预报有降雨，阿拉比卡咖啡涨势暂停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/arabica-coffee-pauses-rally-as-rain-forecast-in-parts-of-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉比卡咖啡价格有所回落，因为天气预报显示，主要咖啡生产国巴西的部分地区将有降雨，而该地区最近一直面临持续炎热干燥的天气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/arabica-coffee-pauses-rally-as-rain-forecast-in-parts-of-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 12:48:03 GMT</pubDate>
